OL,3,CStandards Committee recommends
OL,4,Csanction against Steve Aiken
OL,6,FIt centred around claims that Dr Aiken
OL,7,Fhad raised a complaint that he had
OL,8,Fmade about Mr McHugh, alleging the
OL,9,FSinn Fein politician or his office had
OL,10,Fnot made a declaration of interest
OL,11,Frelating to being in receipt of a
OL,12,Fsmall business grant loan during
OL,13,Fsittings involving the Land and
OL,14,FProperty Services or the Department of
OL,15,FFinance.
OL,17,FMr McHugh said that Dr Aiken's
OL,18,Fdisclosure of both the fact and the
OL,19,Fcontents of the complaint were in
OL,20,Fbreach of members' rules.
