OL,3,CStandards Committee recommends
OL,4,Csanction against Steve Aiken
OL,6,FThe complaint was investigated by the
OL,7,Findependent Assembly Commissioner for
OL,8,FStandards Dr Melissa McCullough.
OL,10,FFollowing consideration of her
OL,11,Finvestigation report, in March 2022,
OL,12,Fthe then Standards Committee concluded
OL,13,Fthat Dr Aiken had breached the code
OL,14,Fthrough the unauthorised disclosure of
OL,15,Fconfidential information relating to a
OL,16,Flive complaint and by failing to co-
OL,17,Foperate at all times with the
OL,18,Fcommissioner's investigation.
