OL,3,CStandards Committee recommends
OL,4,Csanction against Steve Aiken
OL,6,FIt said Dr Aiken, as a member of the
OL,7,FStandards Committee, should have been
OL,8,F"leading by example".
OL,10,FA successive Standards Committee has
OL,11,Frecommended the sanction that Dr Aiken
OL,12,Fbe excluded from Assembly proceedings
OL,13,Ffor a period of two sitting days.
