OL,3,CStandards Committee recommends
OL,4,Csanction against Steve Aiken
OL,6,FThe current committee chairperson Sinn
OL,7,FFein MLA Caral Ni Chuilin said:
OL,8,F"Whilst the committee takes all
OL,9,Fbreaches of the code very seriously,
OL,10,Fit noted the conclusion of the last
OL,11,Fcommittee that this was an egregious
OL,12,Fbreach given the particular
OL,13,Fcircumstances of the case.
OL,15,F"I am therefore pleased that the
OL,16,Fcommittee has agreed to recommend to
OL,17,Fthe Assembly that it imposes what we
OL,18,Fconsider to be an appropriate and
OL,19,Fproportionate sanction."
